text: Jihara bade cage raha ute calada hai tam uha apane la'i hi calada hai ate jihara bada galata raha apana'unda hai uha khuda apane nukasana la'i zimevara huda hai. Ate ko'i bhara cukana vala kise duje da bhara nahim cukega. Ate asim kade udom taka saza nahim dide jadom taka asim kise rasula nu na bheji'e
